### Managing EC2 via CLI
- Start instance: `aws ec2 start-instances --instance-ids <id>`
- Stop instance: `aws ec2 stop-instances --instance-ids <id>`
- Open security group port: `aws ec2 authorize-security-group-ingress --group-id <sg> --protocol tcp --port 22 --cidr 0.0.0.0/0`
- List all: `aws ec2 describe-instances --query 'Reservations[*].Instances[*].[Tags[?Key=\`Name\`].Value|[0],State.Name,PublicIpAddress]' --output table`

